Feature: Making a move

    Scenario: Player makes a valid move
        Given a game is in progress
        And the current player is 1
        And square 2 is unoccupied
        When player makes a move at 2
        Then square 2 is occupied by 1

    Scenario: Player makes an invalid move
        Given a game is in progress
        And the current player is 1
        And square 5 is occupied
        When player makes a move at 5
        Then square 5 is occupied by 1

    Scenario: Player makes a move out of board
        Given a game is in progress
        And the current player is 1
        When player makes a move at 12
        Then the game breaks
